blog.description: Mostly a Taylor Swift/Gaylor Swift blog. Fell down the Kaylor rabbit hole shortly after Rep came out and everything clicked 🌈

body:
Fun little thought about “I’d Lie”

Another cool thing to consider is the possibility that Taylor is using the term “I’d lie” to be blatantly honest here but lead the listener to make a common assumption. The assumption is that she’d lie and say she doesn’t love him despite knowing everything about him. But what if it’s the opposite. She knows all these things about this guy like his favorite color and his birthday, his personality and his family, but when asked if she loves him she’d lie and say YES because that’s what she’s supposed to say, but she doesn’t love him because well it’s just fake and she’s playing a role. She is a lyrical genius after all!!!! 😉
